headline: 2 Bargain Stocks That Could Double Your Money
summary: Krispy Kreme offers substantial upside if management can stabilize sales and reduce debt.  Lululemon's premium brand positioning in the sports apparel market is significantly undervalued.  Krispy Kreme (NASDAQ: DNUT) stock is down 67% over the past year due to weak financial results, but the stock could soar if management's moves to improve profitability pay off.
